data.description: Great location!  Close to town. Desirable classic Copper Canyon fenced home. FOUR bedroom two full bathroom home with open floor plan layout.  Spacious home with plenty of room to entertain or relax with family.  Kitchen has an island and an abundance of cabinets. Large master suite with walk-in closet.  Ceiling fans throughout the home. 2-car garage with shelves. East facing porch for relaxing.  Sizable roomy storage shed in back yard. Refrigerator doesn't convey.
